Copy by value and references

only primitve data types are involved...
primitve:Number,String Boolean.

Copy by references
non-primitve:array and objects

rest and spread parameter(ES6)

Spread operator: ...

Rest parameter:...restparamname
usage: in functions 

array destructuring

unpacking array elements into bunch of variables
destructuring:unpacking

ForEach:

1.it will be applicable to array
2.it will take function as a parameter
3.it will also apply on each and every element of array
4. return type undefined

Syntax:arrayname.forEach();


For of

:it is used to print the elements in the array

for(variable of arrayname)


Only for forward iteration


only for array

Template literals:ES6

